commit_message: Merge pull request #492 from sam575/patch-1 Fix rgb -> bgr while image loading and displaying

Fix rgb -> bgr while image loading and displaying cap.read() returns BGR image.
So rgb->bgr is only needed for scipy.misc.imread 

cv2.imshow expects BGR image for displaying properly(RGB)
Refer: http://stackoverflow.com/a/15074748/1134940
